PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1996-1195 of August 7, 1996 which appointed the following persons as members of the Farm Debt Review Board for the Province of Alberta by revoking the words "for a term ending December 31, 1996" and substituting the words "for a term ending July 31, 1997".
